Package Presentation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddMoneyComand  
    CheckoutCommand
    Receives request from products.jsp, gets shoppingcart-session, calculates lineitem-price, checks if balance is sufficient, if yes withdraws price from balance, inserts order in database and forwards to confirmation.jsp, if no forwards to insufficient_funds.jsp.
    Command
    Command is the abstract base class for all Commands, including the abstract execute method, which receives and processes requests from jsp pages and forwards to jsp pages.
    DefaultCommand  
    FrontController  
    LoginCommand
    Receives input from login.jsp, validates this input with the use of methods from LoginController, and eventually, if the input is valid, creates a session with the user and forwards user to index.jsp.
    LogoutCommand  
    RegisterCommand
    Receives input from registration.jsp, validates this input with the use of methods from LoginController, PasswordChecker and UsernameChecker, and eventually, if the input is valid, inserts user with given input to database and redirects to login.jsp.
    ShopCommand
    Receives request from products.jsp, creates shoppingcart session, Topping, Bottom, LineItem, and ShoppingCart object and adds LineItem to ShoppingCart.
    TEST  
    TESTOB  
    UnknownCommand
